寒武纪生命大爆发
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">外文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
Cambrian Explosion
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">性    质</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
古生物学和地质学上的一大悬案
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">起    源</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
埃迪卡拉动物群
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">代    表</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
云南澄江生物群
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">发生时间</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
寒武纪
</dd>
</dl></div>
